<i>Kimhan, a cool professional model.</i>

11
00:00:51,080 --> 00:00:54,200
<i>Lincoln, a determined Asian-German guy.</i>

12
00:00:54,280 --> 00:00:57,880
<i>And Wigrom, the ultimate entertainer.</i>

13
